high_descs: Go left and face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick the large knife up from the counter.
Slice the bread on the counter.
Turn and face the counter to the left.
Put the large knife down in front of the other knife.
Turn and face the counter to the right again.
Pick a slice of bread up from the counter.
Move to the right and stand in front of the microwave.
Put the bread in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and take the bread out and shut the door.
Turn to the left and then go forward and right and then right again to go around the counter and turn to the right to face the trash can.
Put the bread in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of bread in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Cut the loaf of bread on the counter.
Turn to the left to face the counter.
Place the knife below the other knife on the counter.
Turn right to face the bread on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Take a step to the right to face the microwave on the counter.
Heat the slice of bread in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and walk forward and then right around the counter to face the trash can on the opposite end of the room.
Place the slice of bread in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To heat a slice of bread as well as place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Go to the counter left of the stove
Pick up the knife
Cut the loaf of bread
Turn to the left
Place the knife down near the other knife
Turn to the bread
Pick up a slice of bread
Go to the microwave
Heat the slice of bread
Go to the black bin
Put the bread in the bin
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of bread in a bin
